reviewText: I have seen the movie many times before but this copy was in black and white.
Terrible Picture quality, I, Personally didn't want to continue to watch .....

The Video quality wasn't great.  But it has allot more legitimate Depth and Character development then you generally expect form these Italian Sword and Sandal films.

Semiramis starts a very sexy scheming Femme Fatale, but becomes a very sympathetic noble Queen.

I highly recommend it.
